Run
1) Download binary and Models file 
	https://bitbucket.org/krha/cloudlet-applications/get/master.tar.gz (9.7 MB)

2) Install runtime library
	sudo apt-get install libcv4 libhighgui4 libcvaux4 libdevil1c2 libglut3 libglew1.5	(17.8 MB)	

Compile
1) Install dev library
	sudo apt-get install build-essential g++ git-core gitk
	sudo apt-get install libcv-dev libglew-dev libdevil-dev libhighgui-dev libglut3-dev

2) Download source file
	git clone git@bitbucket.org:krha/cloudlet-applications.git
	

